Interval Shooter
By Sam Von Ehren
gamesketches.wordpress.com
-----------------------------------------------------------

This is a music creation experience that works within the
framework of a shooter. The player flies around and shoots
enemies, everytime they kill one it plays a note in the C
Major scale. If the player gets hit by a ship the game ends.

Controls
-----------------------------------------------------------
The player moves the ship with the standard ASDW controls or
with the arrow keys. To fire a shot, the player presses Q.


